OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783682373
OL,3,CBoy arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter woman dies
OL,6,FA teenage boy has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder after the death of
OL,8,Fa woman in her 60s.
OL,10,FOfficers responded to reports of a
OL,11,Fdisturbance in Burnage, Manchester on
OL,12,FWednesday 8 July at around 8am.
OL,14,FA woman died at the scene at an
OL,15,Faddress on Ivylea Road.
OL,17,FA 16-year-old boy remains in custody
OL,18,Ffor further questioning.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
