OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1783682373
OL,3,CBoy arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,4,Cafter woman dies
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Sean McFadden from
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police said: "We
OL,8,Funderstand this will have caused some
OL,9,Flocal concern around the community,
OL,10,Fbut I want to reassure you we believe
OL,11,Fthis to be an isolated incident.
OL,13,F"We currently have a boy in custody
OL,14,Fand we ask people to not speculate as
OL,15,Fwe continue our investigation to
OL,16,Festablish the full circumstances of
OL,17,Fthis incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
